### GET request to example server
### 1. All 2024 Race sessions
GET https://api.openf1.org/v1/sessions?year=2024

###

### 2. Hamilton telemetry (Bahrain 2024 Race)
GET https://api.openf1.org/v1/drivers?session_key=9472
###

### 3. Verstappen telemetry (Bahrain 2024 Race)
GET https://api.openf1.org/v1/laps?session_key=9472&driver_number=44

###